{"tid":2418701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佩洛西：審訊李柱銘等香港泛民領袖是侮辱法治「須考慮所有追究北京責任的選項」","createTime":"2021-02-22T23:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T01:40:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"da554970738889c29abc9c01735bbc91ab67f99c","tid":2418701,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T23:12:37.000Z","msg":"李柱銘、黎智英等9名香港泛民主派人士，被控前年8.18維園民陣集會後非法組織和參與遊行，案件正在審訊之際，美國眾議院議長裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）周一（2/22）發表聲明，呼籲追究北京壓制香港的責任。<br />\n<br />\n裴洛西在聲明中指出，「李柱銘是勇氣和原則的化身，其鍥而不捨而和平地爭取在香港以至整個中國促進自治與民主自由，啟發了全球熱愛自由的人。審訊李柱銘及其他泛民領袖是侮辱法治，並發出北京會不擇手段壓制香港人權利與自由的可怕訊息。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n她說，「中國政府必須知道世界正在看著其扼殺人權，我們必須考慮所有向中國追究責任的選項。」<br />\n<br />\n裴洛西說，「如果我們因為商業利益而不就中國人權大聲疾呼，我們就失去為世界任何地方人權發聲的所有道德權威。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210223/UK6GREMTXBAAZMZV6GAPGDSYMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2FUK6GREMTXBAAZMZV6GAPGDSYMI%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=a7233498\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2FUK6GREMTXBAAZMZV6GAPGDSYMI%2F&h=69111235\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210223/UK6GREMTXBAAZMZV6GAPGDSYMI/</a>"},{"pid":"ad1f0584076840eece9bf30ff046df54c73a906e","tid":2418701,"uid":99962,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T23:14:06.000Z","msg":"西：一直關注事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcad60b4a478e22b0f484307ed0df4665868f4fb","tid":2418701,"uid":266503,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T23:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WATLgeY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWATLgeY.gif&h=9238c5b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9764abb2bbb5cbd61325a1f6792c0e3f0f2d749f","tid":2418701,"uid":48234,"like":15,"dislike":6,"scor